    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I would say so. JDK7 adds the <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/essential/concurrency/forkjoin.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">fork-join framework</a> but that is an enhancement rather than a replacement for earlier concurrency tools.</p>\n"
