    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>While my perspective may be biased, my current intention for updating the book would be almost strictly additive, covering fork-join, parallel decomposition, and the new parallel bulk data operations coming in Java SE 8.</p>\n<p><strong>EDIT 2020:</strong> ... and Project Loom.</p>\n<p><strong>EDIT 2021:</strong> ... and Project Loom :)</p>\n<p><strong>EDIT 2022:</strong> ... and Project Loom !</p>\n"
