    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Yes definitely it's still valid, but I will recommend in addition or as an introduction <a href=\"http://www.manning.com/evans/\"><em>The Well-Grounded Java Developer</em></a> a well written book with a chapter on modern Java concurrency techniques and nicely done examples.</p>\n"
