    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you are going to start your project using Java 8 you might want to consider fresh books and tutorials as well because of new stuff appeared in Java 8 like streams,lambdas and new atomics -  that changes development methods a little bit.</p>\n"
